The shrine enshrines {{ill|Haniyasu-hime|ja|波邇夜須毘売神|12=draft|12=draft}}, a goddess born from the excrement of {{ill|Izanami|ja|伊邪那美|12=draft|12=draft}}, who suffered burns and perished after giving birth to the fire god {{ill|Kagutsuchi|ja|迦具土命|12=draft|12=draft}}. It is said that from her bodily fluids—urine, feces, and vomit—various deities were born, with Haniyasu-hime emerging from her feces.

